S.FORM: Luxembourg Gaga kska Owcow ka Luxembourg, 49 45 N, 6 10 E ka gaga na nniqan. Kana ka knlbangan na o 2,586 sq km(hangan na o Tg179) (knlbanga dxgal o 2,586 sq km, knlbangan qsiya o 0 sq km). Kana ka sejiqun o niqan 582,291 hiyi. Gaga Luxembourg ka pusu alang paru, jiyax 23 idas 6 ka jiyax skrayan klwaan. Manu ka dxgal Luxembourg ga wada sugan 50.70 ka dxgal qpahan, 33.50 ka dxgal bbuyu, rahuq dxgal do niqan 15.80 na. Bukung klwaan ta sayang o kiya ka Henri, pnaah hngkawas2000 idas 10 jiyax 7pnrajing kmlawa klwaan.
